MUST SEE LARGE PRIMARY BEDROOM WITH TWO CLOSETS AND HUGE PRIMARY BATH.  NO CARPET IN HOME. ALL WINDOWS HAVE BLINDS AND PRIVATE COVERED PATIO FOR ENTERTRAINING. HOA FEES INCLUDE: BASIC CABEL, INTERNET, ALARM MONITORING, FULL LAWN MAINTENANCE, EXTERIOR AND INTERIOR PEST CONTROL, CLUBHOUSE, FITNESS CENTER, POOL AND SECURITY. TRADITION FEATURES GREAT DINNING, SHOPPING, AND RECREATIONAL ACTIVITIES FOR THE ENTIRE FAMILY TO ENJOY.
